urdu transliteration text:
ay maa tum mujhe paas bulaalo mujhe pyaassataati heyturbat se ali asghar ki awaaz ye aati hey
Ali Asghar’s voice comes from the grave
@HujjatELC

darwaaze pe khaima ke ye ik bibi khar(r)i heyhyy, mur mur ke jo maqtal ki taraf dekh rahi heyik khoon bharey chole ko aankho(n) seylagaati hey
And holds a blood-stained shirt to hear eyes
@HujjatELC
